## 🏗️ Plan de Sprints

### Sprint A: 🔒 SEGURIDAD (D1, D2, D3, D4) — ~1 semana

> **Por qué primero**: Sin esto, la app es vulnerable. Un inversor lo nota al instante.

#### A1. JWT Verification en Edge Functions (D1)

**Archivos a modificar:**
- [supabase/functions/calculate-payroll/index.ts](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20%281%29/supabase/functions/calculate-payroll/index.ts) — quitar `--no-verify-jwt`, añadir verificación manual
- [supabase/functions/detect-anomalies/index.ts](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20%281%29/supabase/functions/detect-anomalies/index.ts) — idem
- `supabase/config.toml` — quitar flag `--no-verify-jwt`

**Implementación:**
```typescript
// Patrón para CADA Edge Function:
const authHeader = req.headers.get('Authorization');
if (!authHeader) return new Response('Unauthorized', { status: 401 });
const { data: { user }, error } = await supabase.auth.getUser(
  authHeader.replace('Bearer ', '')
);
if (error || !user) return new Response('Forbidden', { status: 403 });
```

#### A2. Secrets Management (D2)

**Archivos a modificar/crear:**
- [DELETE] [.env](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20%281%29/.env) del repositorio (añadir a `.gitignore` si no está)
- [NEW] [.env.example](file:///c:/Users/ibrab/Downloads/app/harvestpro-nz%20%281%29/.env.example) — template sin valores reales
- `vercel.json` — configurar environment variables reference
- Documentar: mover keys a Vercel Dashboard → Environment Variables

#### A3. Content Security Policy (D3)

**Archivos a modificar:**
- `vercel.json` — añadir headers CSP
- `index.html` — añadir meta CSP como fallback

```json
{
  "headers": [{
    "source": "/(.*)",
    "headers": [{
      "key": "Content-Security-Policy",
      "value": "default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'; connect-src 'self' https://*.supabase.co; img-src 'self' data: blob:; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'"
    }, {
      "key": "X-Frame-Options", "value": "DENY"
    }, {
      "key": "X-Content-Type-Options", "value": "nosniff"
    }]
  }]
}
```

#### A4. Input Sanitization con Zod (D4 parcial)

**Archivos a crear:**
- [NEW] `src/schemas/auth.schema.ts` — login, register inputs
- [NEW] `src/schemas/payroll.schema.ts` — payroll calculation inputs
- [NEW] `src/schemas/attendance.schema.ts` — check-in/out inputs
- [NEW] `src/schemas/index.ts` — barrel

**Verificación Sprint A:**
```bash
# Edge Functions responden 401 sin token
curl -X POST https://project.supabase.co/functions/v1/calculate-payroll
# CSP headers presentes
curl -I https://app.harvestpro.nz
```

